messages.message:
I can't say I tried the advanced models - feel free to experiment using this base project @lydia!

The reason is that it introduces more risk of incorrect extractions. Given the current reliability of vision fields, its better to do one extraction followed by many derivations. If I opted for multiple extractions I'd be doing a lot of reasoning and extraction where mistakes could creep in and I'd have to check all the results instead of just the JSON field
